        {
          "key": "5",
          "value": {
            "data": {
              "entityKey": "23967f6b-fcb3-4913-8e4c-fb5b1d8bb39c",
              "markdown": "```bash\n\n| `agent/agent.py` | The agent being optimized (OpenAI Agents SDK template) |\n| `benchmark.py` | Runs your benchmark, returns per-task rewards |\n| `gating.py` | Two-step gate: eval suite pass rate + full `val_score` |\n| `record.py` | Appends iteration results to `workspace/results.tsv` |\n| `workspace/suite.json` | Regression suite — maintained by the coding agent, not you |\n| `workspace/learnings.md` | Persistent log: what worked, what didn't, what the agent needs from you |\n| `PROGRAM.md` | Instructions the coding agent follows — where you steer the loop |\n```"
            },
            "mutability": "Mutable",
            "type": "MARKDOWN"
          }
        },
